@node Main "Bobarr - Documentation"

                              'Bobarr' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Bobarr' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} where you have to move all the bars
that are shown on the 7 by 7 spaces board. It is based on the usual
'Sliding-bars' puzzles, but Bobarr offers a variation: in addition to
horizontal and vertical bars, there are also diagonal bars that have
to be moved. Each type of bar can be moved in the directions its shape
represent... if the empty space is located in line and next to that
bar.

  Another feature is that any bar located at the edge of the board can
move to the other side... if, of course, the empty space is on the
other side and in line with that bar.

  Complete the game in the least amount of moves possible.

  Have fun!

